            "Keep your code organized from the start",
            "Document everything - future you will thank you"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        type: 'conclusion',
        content: {
          title: "The Power of AI-Assisted Development üöÄ",
          sections: [
            {
              text: "Looking back, AI has been an incredible partner in developing these tools. It helped me understand Nuke's Python API, suggested better approaches, and caught potential issues before they became problems.",
